                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Siste viator iter animum<supplied reason="lost">que intende sepu</supplied>lchro <lb n="2"/>et lege quam dure sit mihi v<supplied reason="lost">ita d</supplied>ata ipso im<lb break="no" n="3"/>marcebam florenti <note>sic</note> caro m<supplied reason="lost">ari</supplied>to in XIIII <lb n="4"/>annum mors mihi saeva fuit <supplied reason="lost">nam d</supplied>isceptarunt <lb n="5"/>fata ne pia esse patri nec mat<supplied reason="lost">ri possem</supplied> te&amp;lt;n=M&amp;gt;<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>r</abbr><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="6"/>pi<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> faemin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> cast<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> pro piet<supplied reason="lost">as! inter p</supplied>rimas <lb n="7"/>satiavi fata superba nomine V<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="8"/>rest<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>tu</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied><expan><abbr>bar</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan> qui nunc quam sci<supplied reason="lost">s raptam illa sed</supplied> <lb n="9"/>ab impia fata disceptata die ut n<supplied reason="lost">ondum coniuncta</supplied> <lb n="10"/>marito crudelis thalamos post mor<supplied reason="lost">tem invita</supplied> <lb n="11"/>reliqui teque <expan><abbr>rog</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> comis <expan><abbr>dolea</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> tibi pulch<supplied reason="lost">rius illud</supplied> <lb n="12"/>quod mea virginitas mor<supplied reason="lost">tal</supplied>i somn<supplied reason="lost">o abolevit</supplied> <lb n="13"/>isque tuas cineres aurea terr<supplied reason="lost">a teget ast hoc tantum vos</supplied> <lb n="14"/>ego nunc moneo genitore<supplied reason="lost">s quid fletis nam fata potest quis</supplied> <lb n="15"/>rumpere nemo <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><ce